edu.regis.msse670.invenstory.domain

Class BasicInventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.regis.msse670.invenstory.domain.Inventory
      • edu.regis.msse670.invenstory.domain.BasicInventory

  • public class BasicInventory
extends Inventory
    BasicInventory is the most basic implementation of the Inventory abstact class. It contains a unique identifying name, a tier and a Storable array. The inventoryMax and inventoryStored ints are used to limit and track the contents of the array respectively. This object will make up the bulk of a fully populated WorldInventory.
